<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Heightmap Downloader</title>

<script src='https://api.tiles.mapbox.com/mapbox-gl-js/v1.8.0/mapbox-gl.js'></script>
<link href='https://api.tiles.mapbox.com/mapbox-gl-js/v1.8.0/mapbox-gl.css' rel='stylesheet' />
<script src="https://unpkg.com/mapbox-gl-geocoder@4.7.2/dist/mapbox-gl-geocoder.min.js"></script>
<link href="https://unpkg.com/mapbox-gl-geocoder@4.7.2/dist/mapbox-gl-geocoder.css" rel="stylesheet" />
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jszip/3.10.1/jszip.min.js"></script>

<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&family=Syne:wght@400;700;800&display=swap');

  :root {
    --bg: #0a0a0f;
    --surface: #12121a;
    --border: #1e1e2e;
    --accent: #00ff88;
    --accent2: #0088ff;
    --accent3: #ff8800;
    --text: #e8e8f0;
    --muted: #5a5a7a;
    --danger: #ff4444;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    height: 100vh;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  #map { flex: 1; width: 100%; }

  .panel {
    position: absolute;
    top: 12px;
    right: 16px;
    z-index: 10;
    width: 290px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .panel-header {
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .panel-body {
    padding: 16px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .coord-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .coord-item {
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 8px 10px;
  }

  .coord-label {
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .coord-value {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .field-label {
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  /* ── 좌표 직접 입력 섹션 ── */
  .coord-input-section {
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
  }

  .coord-input-section .field-label {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: var(--accent2);
  }

  .coord-input-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .coord-input-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .coord-input-label {
    font-size: 8px;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .coord-input {
    width: 100%;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 6px 8px;
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text);
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .coord-input:focus {
    border-color: var(--accent2);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(0,136,255,0.15);
  }

  .coord-input::placeholder {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 10px;
  }

  .coord-input.error {
    border-color: var(--danger);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(255,68,68,0.15);
  }

  .coord-go-btn {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 8px;
    background: var(--accent2);
    color: var(--bg);
    border: none;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .coord-go-btn::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .coord-go-btn:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
  .coord-go-btn:active { transform: scale(0.98); }

  .coord-error-msg {
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--danger);
    margin-top: 4px;
    min-height: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  /* ── end 좌표 직접 입력 ── */

  .grid-size-wrap {
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
  }

  .grid-size-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .grid-size-label {
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .grid-size-badge {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--accent);
    background: rgba(0,255,136,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,136,0.25);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .grid-tick-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .grid-tick {
    font-size: 8px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .info-box {
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 10px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .info-box .coord-label { margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .info-box .coord-value { font-size: 15px; }

  .height-info {
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 10px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .height-item .h-label {
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .height-item .h-value {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .download-btn {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 14px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .download-btn::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .download-btn:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
  .download-btn:active { transform: scale(0.98); }

  .download-btn:disabled {
    background: var(--border) !important;
    color: var(--muted) !important;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }

  .download-btn:disabled::before { display: none; }

  .btn-png { background: var(--accent); color: var(--bg); }
  .btn-raw { background: var(--accent3); color: var(--bg); }
  .btn-overview { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8800ff, #4400cc); color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 3px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .btn-overview::before { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.2s; }
  .btn-overview:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
  .btn-overview:active { transform: scale(0.98); }
  .btn-overview:disabled { background: var(--border) !important; color: var(--muted) !important; cursor: not-allowed; }
  .btn-overview:disabled::before { display: none; }

  .btn-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .btn-row .download-btn {
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 12px 6px;
  }

  .progress-wrap {
    display: none;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .progress-wrap.visible { display: flex; }

  .progress-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .progress-bar-bg {
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--border);
    border-radius: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .progress-bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent2), var(--accent));
    width: 0%;
    transition: width 0.3s;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .status {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-align: center;
    min-height: 14px;
  }

  .status.ok  { color: var(--accent); }
  .status.err { color: var(--danger); }

  .geocoder-wrap {
    position: absolute;
    top: 12px;
    left: 16px;
    z-index: 10;
    width: 260px;
  }

  .mapboxgl-ctrl-geocoder {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace !important;
    background: var(--surface) !important;
    border: 1px solid var(--border) !important;
    border-radius: 4px !important;
    box-shadow: none !important;
    min-width: 100% !important;
    width: 100% !important;
  }

  .mapboxgl-ctrl-geocoder input {
    background: transparent !important;
    color: var(--text) !important;
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace !important;
    font-size: 12px !important;
  }

  .mapboxgl-ctrl-geocoder input::placeholder { color: var(--muted) !important; }

  .mapboxgl-ctrl-geocoder .suggestions {
    background: var(--surface) !important;
    border: 1px solid var(--border) !important;
    border-radius: 3px !important;
  }

  .mapboxgl-ctrl-geocoder .suggestions li a {
    color: var(--text) !important;
    font-size: 11px !important;
  }

  .legend {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 32px;
    left: 16px;
    z-index: 10;
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .legend-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .legend-color {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  #loading-overlay {
    display: none;
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(10,10,15,0.7);
    z-index: 50;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
  }

  #loading-overlay.visible { display: flex; }

  .loading-box {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 28px 36px;
    text-align: center;
    min-width: 340px;
    max-width: 420px;
  }

  .pipeline-steps {
    margin: 14px 0 10px;
    text-align: left;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .pipe-step {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    opacity: 0.35;
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
  }
  .pipe-step.active { opacity: 1; }
  .pipe-step.done   { opacity: 0.65; }
  .pipe-dot {
    width: 7px; height: 7px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--muted);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: background 0.3s;
  }
  .pipe-step.active .pipe-dot { background: var(--accent2); box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--accent2); }
  .pipe-step.done   .pipe-dot { background: var(--accent); }
  .pipe-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .pipe-desc {
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-left: 4px;
  }

  .load-progress-wrap {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin: 10px 0 4px;
  }
  .load-progress-bg {
    flex: 1;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--border);
    border-radius: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .load-progress-fill {
    height: 100%;
    width: 0%;
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: width 0.3s ease;
  }
  .load-progress-label {
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--muted);
    min-width: 28px;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .loading-spinner {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-top-color: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: spin 0.8s linear infinite;
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
  }

  @keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

  .loading-text {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .loading-sub {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .tile-grid-wrap { margin-top: 12px; }

  .tile-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .tile-cell {
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    background: var(--border);
    border-radius: 1px;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .tile-cell.done    { background: var(--accent); }
  .tile-cell.active  { background: var(--accent2); animation: pulse 0.6s infinite alternate; }
  .tile-cell.error   { background: var(--danger); }

  @keyframes pulse { to { opacity: 0.4; } }

  .hint {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 32px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    z-index: 10;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: opacity 0.5s;
  }

  .hint.hide { opacity: 0; }

  .format-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 6px;
    padding: 2px 10px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  .format-badge.png { background: rgba(0,255,136,0.15); color: var(--accent); border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,136,0.3); }
  .format-badge.raw { background: rgba(255,136,0,0.15); color: var(--accent3); border: 1px solid rgba(255,136,0,0.3); }

  /* ── 확인 모달 ── */
  #confirm-modal {
    display: none;
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 60;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(10,10,15,0.75);
    backdrop-filter: blur(3px);
  }
  #confirm-modal.visible { display: flex; }
  .confirm-box {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 28px 32px;
    min-width: 320px;
    max-width: 400px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .confirm-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .confirm-desc {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .confirm-desc span { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; }
  .confirm-btns {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .confirm-btn {
    padding: 11px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: opacity 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
  }
  .confirm-btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
  .confirm-btn:active { transform: scale(0.97); }
  .confirm-btn-ok     { background: var(--accent3); color: var(--bg); }
  .confirm-btn-cancel { background: var(--border);  color: var(--muted); }

</style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="map"></div>

<div class="geocoder-wrap" id="geocoder"></div>

<div class="panel">
  <div class="panel-header">Export Settings</div>
  <div class="panel-body">

    <div class="coord-row">
      <div class="coord-item">
        <div class="coord-label">LNG</div>
        <div class="coord-value" id="disp-lng">—</div>
      </div>
      <div class="coord-item">
        <div class="coord-label">LAT</div>
        <div class="coord-value" id="disp-lat">—</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── 위도/경도 직접 입력 섹션 ── -->
    <div class="coord-input-section">
      <div class="field-label">▸ 좌표 직접 입력</div>
      <div class="coord-input-row">
        <div class="coord-input-group">
          <div class="coord-input-label">위도 (LAT)</div>
          <input
            class="coord-input"
            id="input-lat"
            type="number"
            step="any"
            min="-90"
            max="90"
            placeholder="-90 ~ 90"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="coord-input-group">
          <div class="coord-input-label">경도 (LNG)</div>
          <input
            class="coord-input"
            id="input-lng"
            type="number"
            step="any"
            min="-180"
            max="180"
            placeholder="-180 ~ 180"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <button class="coord-go-btn" onclick="applyCoordInput()">↗ 이동 &amp; 선택</button>
      <div class="coord-error-msg" id="coord-error"></div>
    </div>
    <!-- ── end 직접 입력 ── -->

    <div>
      <div class="field-label">Output</div>
      <div class="info-box">
        <div class="coord-label">3 × 3 tiles &nbsp;|&nbsp; 1024 × 1024 px / tile</div>
        <div class="coord-value" style="font-size:15px; margin-top:4px;" id="info-total-km">9.216 km × 9.216 km</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="height-info">
      <div class="height-item">
        <div class="h-label">Min Height</div>
        <div class="h-value" id="disp-min">— m</div>
      </div>
      <div class="height-item">
        <div class="h-label">Max Height</div>
        <div class="h-value" id="disp-max">— m</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="progress-wrap" id="progress-wrap">
      <div class="progress-label" id="progress-label">처리 중...</div>
      <div class="progress-bar-bg">
        <div class="progress-bar-fill" id="progress-fill"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="btn-row">
      <button class="download-btn btn-png" id="dl-btn-png" onclick="startDownload('png')">
        ↓ PNG ZIP
      </button>
      <button class="download-btn btn-raw" id="dl-btn-raw" onclick="startDownload('raw')">
        ↓ RAW ZIP
      </button>
    </div>
    <div class="status" id="status-msg" style="font-size:9px; text-align:center; color:var(--muted);">
      PNG: Mapbox RGB 재인코딩 &nbsp;|&nbsp; RAW: 24-bit R·G·B 원본
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top:10px; border-top:1px solid var(--border); padding-top:10px;">
      <div class="field-label" style="margin-bottom:6px;">Overview (512×512 · 1px=1mpp)</div>
      <button class="download-btn btn-overview" id="dl-btn-overview" onclick="startOverviewDownload()"
        style="width:100%; font-size:11px; padding:10px;">
        ↓ Overview PNG
      </button>
      <div class="status" id="status-overview" style="font-size:9px; margin-top:4px; color:var(--muted);">
        중심 타일 1장 · elev + normal
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top:10px; border-top:1px solid var(--border); padding-top:10px;">
      <div class="field-label" style="margin-bottom:6px;">Mega Map (9216×9216 · 보라색 그리드)</div>
      <button class="download-btn btn-overview" id="dl-btn-mega" onclick="startMegaMapDownload()"
        style="width:100%; font-size:11px; padding:10px; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#cc6600,#994400);">
        ↓ Mega Map PNG
      </button>
      <div class="status" id="status-mega" style="font-size:9px; margin-top:4px; color:var(--muted);">
        9,216m × 9,216m · 3×3 그리드 선 포함
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="status" id="status-result">지도를 클릭하여 중심 위치를 선택하세요</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="legend">
  <div class="legend-item">
    <div class="legend-color" style="background:#888888;"></div>전체 영역
  </div>
  <div class="legend-item">
    <div class="legend-color" style="background:#00cc44;"></div>플레이 영역
  </div>
  <div class="legend-item">
    <div class="legend-color" style="background:#4464e1;"></div>시작 영역
  </div>
</div>

<div class="hint" id="hint">지도를 클릭하거나 좌표를 입력하여 위치 선택</div>

<div id="confirm-modal">
  <div class="confirm-box">
    <div class="confirm-title" id="confirm-title">RAW 다운로드 확인</div>
    <div class="confirm-desc" id="confirm-desc"></div>
    <div class="confirm-btns">
      <button class="confirm-btn confirm-btn-cancel" id="confirm-cancel">취소</button>
